---
title: Cheesy Middle Eastern Lamb Manoush with Fries, Herby Yoghurt & Pickled Veggies
description: These flatbreads are everything you want - savoury, cheesy and crisp! The lamb mince is tender and flavourful, and pairs perfectly with chermoula spices and sesame seeds. All you need are some fun sides like golden potato fries, tangy yoghurt and pickles to seal the deal!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/676912f79bfc6de73c8e4705-a3abdf60.jpeg
